%h1
  Editing your OC

- if @oc.errors.any?
  %h6
    = pluralize(@oc.errors.count, "error")
    stopped me saving this OC.
  %ul
    - @oc.errors.full_messages.each do |msg|
      %li= msg

= form_for(@oc) do |f|
  = render 'fields', f: f

  = f.submit "Save your changes", class: 'btn btn-primary'
